From 6daf7a1172d3f1c792323021a20fa8a1f6cf3ff7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sat, 16 May 2026 12:41:06 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/8] Redesign UI to Foreman v1 design system

Rebases the app on the new "crisp minimal, warm paper, orange surgical"
visual language from the design handoff. Strategy: remap design tokens
and shared @layer component classes so existing markup auto-inherits the
new look, then rewrite the high-impact bespoke screens.

Foundation
- Replace Barlow/forge/amber tokens with Geist/ink/orange/paper in
  tailwind.config.js and globals.css. Keep legacy aliases (forge, amber,
  mist, chalk, surface, font-display) pointing at v1 values so pages that
  still reference them cascade to the redesign.
- Port the v1 atom library (.fm, .pill, .card, .btn, .stat-grid, .sched,
  .doc, .mw, .portal, .auth-wrap, .land, etc.) into globals.css.
- Rewrite .surface-card, .action-button-primary/secondary/dark,
  .page-title and friends to v1 spec; pages built on these primitives
  pick up hairline borders, paper backgrounds, and orange accents
  without changes.

Bespoke screen rewrites
- OwnerShell: dark v1 sidebar with mono nav labels, brand mark, active
  indicator rail; matching mobile drawer.
- Owner overview: page-h header, stat-grid, today's jobs row pattern,
  WO decision queue, ready-to-bill / overdue / draft cards, metrics rail.
- Worker layout + WorkerTabBar (new client component) for active state.
- Worker dashboard: mw mobile shell with greeting, job cards, sections.
- ClockWidget: dark clock-card with mono timer and orange GO button.
- WorkerJobDetail header + clock panel restyled.
- PortalDashboard: v1 ptop header and sticky tab bar with badge pills.
- Owner schedule day headers retoned to orange-soft.
- Auth set (login, signup, forgot-password, reset-password): two-pane
  auth-wrap layout with dark side panel and clean form column.
- not-found and unauthorized pages on paper with v1 buttons.
